The paper discusses a novel bottom-up Datalog evaluation strategy for debugging, which is a topic related to database systems (cs.DB) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also mentions the integration of the technique into Souffle, a Datalog engine, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE). The use of parallel data structures for achieving high performance is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and cryptography (cs.CR).
